posts.content: Book now for V Dub Drive 2014 - a free aircooled only event in Buxton, Derbyshire on Sunday August 10. We'll have entertainment, trophies, a mini cruise and a display of scooters. See our Facebook page www.facebook.com/vdubdrive2014 for more information and let us know if you want to bring your VW or classic scooter. Hope to see you then!
